{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 51,
    "name": "سُورَةُ الذَّارِيَاتِ",
    "englishName": "Adh-Dhaariyat",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Winnowing Winds",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 60,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 4676,
        "text": "By the winds that scatter the dust,",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 520,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4677,
        "text": "and those that bear the burden [of the rain],",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 520,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4678,
        "text": "and those speeding along with ease,",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 520,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4679,
        "text": "and distributing the command of God at His behest!",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 520,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4680,
        "text": "What you are promised is certainly true:",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 520,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4681,
        "text": "the Judgement will surely come to pass --",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 520,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4682,
        "text": "by the heaven full of tracks,",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4683,
        "text": "surely you are deeply at variance [as to what to believe] --",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4684,
        "text": "he is turned away from [the truth] who is destined to be so turned away.",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4685,
        "text": "May the conjecturers perish,",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4686,
        "text": "who flounder in the depths of ignorance.",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4687,
        "text": "They ask, \"When will the Day of Judgement come?\"",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4688,
        "text": "It will be the Day when they are tormented at the Fire.",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4689,
        "text": "\"Taste your trial. This is what you sought to hasten.\"",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4690,
        "text": "Surely the God-fearing will find themselves in the midst of gardens and springs.",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4691,
        "text": "They shall receive what their Lord will bestow on them. They have done good works in the past,",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4692,
        "text": "sleeping little in the night-time,",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4693,
        "text": "praying at dawn for God's pardon,",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4694,
        "text": "and sharing their possessions with the beggars and the deprived.",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4695,
        "text": "On the earth, and in yourselves,",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4696,
        "text": "there are signs for firm believers. Do you not see then?",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4697,
        "text": "In heaven is your sustenance, and also that which you are promised.",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4698,
        "text": "By the Lord of the heaven and the earth, it is certainly the truth. It is as true as your ability to speak.",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4699,
        "text": "Have you heard the story of Abraham's honoured guests?",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4700,
        "text": "When they came to him they said, \"Peace!\" He answered, \"Peace!\" [saying to himself]. \"They are strangers.\"",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4701,
        "text": "Then he turned quickly to his household, and brought a fatted calf,",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4702,
        "text": "and placed it before them. \"Will you not eat?\" he said,",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4703,
        "text": "beginning to be afraid of them. But they said, \"Don't be afraid\"; and they gave him the good news of a son who would be endowed with knowledge.",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4704,
        "text": "Then his wife came forward, crying and beating her brow. She said, \"I am surely a barren, old woman.\"",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4705,
        "text": "\"Such is the will of your Lord,\" they replied. \"He is the Wise, the All Knowing.\"",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4706,
        "text": "Abraham asked, \"What is your errand, O messengers?\"",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4707,
        "text": "They replied, \"We have been sent to a sinful people,",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4708,
        "text": "so that we may bring down upon them a shower of stones of clay,",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4709,
        "text": "which are marked by your Lord for the punishment of those guilty of excesses.\"",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4710,
        "text": "We saved all the faithful in the town.",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4711,
        "text": "We found in it only one household of true believers --",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4712,
        "text": "and We left therein a sign for those who fear a painful punishment.",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4713,
        "text": "There is another sign in Moses: We sent him to Pharaoh with clear authority.",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4714,
        "text": "But he turned his back, he and his courtiers, and said, \"This is a sorcerer or a madman.\"",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4715,
        "text": "Then We seized him and his army and cast them all into the sea: he himself [Pharaoh] was to blame.",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4716,
        "text": "There is another sign in the [tribe of] 'Ad, when We sent against them a life-destroying wind",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4717,
        "text": "and it destroyed everything over which it passed and reduced it to dust.",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4718,
        "text": "In the Thamud [there was another sign], when they were told, \"Make the most of your lives for a while.\"",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4719,
        "text": "But they rebelled against the command of their Lord. So the thunderbolt overtook them while they looked on:",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4720,
        "text": "they could not stand up again, nor could they defend themselves.",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4721,
        "text": "[We destroyed] the people of Noah before them. They were certainly a sinful people.",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4722,
        "text": "We built the universe with Our might, giving it its vast expanse.",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4723,
        "text": "We have spread out the earth, how well We have spread it out,",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4724,
        "text": "and We created pairs of all things so that you might reflect.",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4725,
        "text": "Therefore hasten to God; truly, I am sent by Him to give you clear warning.",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4726,
        "text": "Do not set up another god, along with God. I come from Him to warn you plainly.",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4727,
        "text": "Likewise, there came no messenger to those before them, but they said, \"He is a sorcerer or a madman.\"",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4728,
        "text": "Have they handed this down to one another? They are certainly a people who exceed all bounds,",
        "numberInSurah": 53,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4729,
        "text": "so ignore them, you are not to blame,",
        "numberInSurah": 54,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4730,
        "text": "but keep on exhorting them, for exhortation benefits the believers.",
        "numberInSurah": 55,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4731,
        "text": "I created the jinn and mankind only so that they might worship Me:",
        "numberInSurah": 56,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4732,
        "text": "I seek no sustenance from them, nor do I want them to feed Me --",
        "numberInSurah": 57,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4733,
        "text": "it is God who is the great Sustainer, the Mighty One, the Invincible.",
        "numberInSurah": 58,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4734,
        "text": "The wrongdoers will meet the same fate as their predecessors, let them not ask Me to hasten on [the punishment],",
        "numberInSurah": 59,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4735,
        "text": "woe, then, to those who are bent on denying the truth, when the Day arrives which they have been promised.",
        "numberInSurah": 60,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
    "edition": {
      "identifier": "en.wahiduddin",
      "language": "en",
      "name": "Wahiduddin Khan",
      "englishName": "Wahiduddin Khan",
      "format": "text",
      "type": "translation",
      "direction": "ltr"
    }
  }
}